					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Yeah, I'm completely baffled by it. I'm surprised how often I seem to get repeating 4 bit or 8 bit patterns, in many different arrangements. Every now and then it looks completely random, but most of the time it's got patterned groups-- but what really surprises me is how the patterns change! Maybe it has to do with the physical organization of the chip itself, like it seems like often every 16th bit has mostly the same value, or every 16th or 32nd byte has the same group, etc, but not always! Sometimes it's a pattern in mosty columns and then one column or a few columns are completely random looking.</div>

